headline.main: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances
headline.print_headline: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances

lead_paragraph: Feyonda Fitzgerald poured in a conference tournament-record 30 points and had seven assists as 25th-ranked Temple defeated Houston on Saturday in the quarterfinals of the American Athletic Conference tournament.
